{"tid":877043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【支爆發窮惡】譚耀宗引述支那官員　居支那港人需跟新安排繳稅","createTime":"2018-10-26T05:06:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T12:21:02.000Z","uid":37661,"like":84,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"25a328135373282a59291f02047d5f8c0ce7d786","tid":877043,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T05:06:28.000Z","msg":"譚耀宗引述支那官員　居支那港人需跟新安排繳稅<br />\n<br />\n2018-10-26 HKT 12:44<br />\n<br />\n支那明年起實施新的《個人所得稅法修正案》，任何人每年於支那居住滿183天，在全球的收入，包括工資、存款利息、股息、物業收益等，都要按照支那稅率報稅。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，人大常委譚耀宗與國家稅務總局官員會面後，引述對方官員說，香港人一年內在支那居住滿183天，便需要根據支那的稅率繳納個人所得稅，但維持設有5年豁免期。<br />\n<br />\n譚耀宗舉例，如果在第5年離開支那超過30天，便可重新計算5年後才繳納相關稅款，他相信有關安排有很大機會實施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1424983-20181026.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1424983-20181026.htm&d=OAXDN9r%2B%2BFpzZkbuk1XxPpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=c417e868\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1424983-20181026.htm&h=5628b74f\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1424983-20181026.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0ee80183d874317a5fa050575c3fac56e992ab83","tid":877043,"uid":76310,"like":78,"dislike":1,"score":77,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T05:08:13.000Z","msg":"絕對支持<br />\n<br />\n依法激稅"},{"pid":"052dc525a23b901e1fe53cb4707f03735263b0f4","tid":877043,"uid":20473,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T05:09:27.000Z","msg":"在中國居住納中國稅天經地義"},{"pid":"793b75b8d0a0cac8d26eef18a1dffc64c4ef09f2","tid":877043,"uid":52006,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T05:11:37.000Z","msg":"共享榮耀，當然要負番義務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"953eeb4f4618172e01cbec622a8c78af7b1d1fd6","tid":877043,"uid":76310,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T05:13:24.000Z","msg":"香港偽人<br />\n香港奶共人仕<br />\